# VDS Global Rules

Shared rules for all DLD projects running on this VDS.
Copied to ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md during setup-vps.sh.

## Git Policy

- Push only to `develop` branch. Never push to `main` directly.
- Conventional Commits format.
- One task = one commit. Tests must pass before committing.

## Quality Rules

- Never mock in integration tests (ADR-013).
- Max 400 LOC per file (600 for tests).
- Max 5 exports in `__init__.py`.
- Explicit error types, no bare exceptions.

## Orchestrator Awareness

- This VDS runs up to 3 concurrent autopilot sessions (2 Claude + 1 Codex).
- Night reviewer runs independently in its own pueue group — do not interfere.
- Max session length: 30 turns.
- QA loop runs after autopilot completes — do not skip.

## Language

Always respond in Russian. Technical terms in English.
